org.apache.ignite.ml.util.generators.primitives.vector

Interface VectorGenerator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Supplier<Vector>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ParametricVectorGenerator, VectorGeneratorsFamily

    public interface VectorGenerator
extends Supplier<Vector>
    Basic interface for pseudo-random vectors generators.
